title: Air Fryer Liners Disposable, Parchment Paper for Baking, 100 Pcs 11 x 9 inch Unbleached Parchment Paper Sheets, Perforated Rectangular Baking Papers, HOFHTD Nonstick Air Fryer Accessories
description:
Our parchment paper for air fryer is suitable for cooking,steaming and baking various types of food,such as meat,pizza,cakes,etc. It's suitable for air fryer,cake pan,metal steamer and oven,etc.
SERVING CHIPS OR OTHER FOOD
Parchment paper can be used to serve Fried foods such as fish and chips, doughnuts, Fried chicken wings, etc. You can also put burgers and other food on it.
BAKING SANDWICHES OR BREAD
Parchment also plays a huge role when you want to take food out, as it does When you make a sandwich in advance to serve as a lunch between classes or want to bring a bread as a snack.
GRILLING MEAT & VEGETABLES
Certain recipes call for parchment paper, which is a heat-resistant, nonstick paper that's used in several ways when cooking and baking. You can also make pouches out of it, called en papillote, to cook fish, chicken, and vegetables.
Warm Tips:
1. The air circulation inside the air fryer is very strong. When you are using it, please put some food on the parchment paper to make sure it will not float up and touch the heating element of the air fryer.
2. The maximum heating time cannot over 45 minutes, and if there is enough food in it, the maximum heating time can be extended by 5 to 15 minutes.
Package includes:
100 x Air Fryer Liners
features: Exclusive Design of Parchment Paper: 11 x 9 inches,compatible with Cuisinart (TOA-60, TOA-65 + more), Breville, Black and Decker, Hamilton Beach, Cosori + more. Measure your appliance before purchasing for best results.
Material: Our Air Fryer Papers are made of wood pulp, oil-proof, waterproof, non-absorbent, and does not dilute at high temperatures. Non-stick and keep your fryer clean.

Heat Resistant: Parchment paper for air fryer temperature resistance is from -68 to 425 degrees fahrenheit. The double silicone coating side keep food out of direct contact with the fryer and cause stains. Easy to clean.

Multi Prepared Holes Design: Our parchment papers have enough holes to help speed up the steam circulation in the air fryer or dehydrators, allowing food to heat fully and evenly without compromising cooking quality.

Warm Tips: Do not add air fryer paper in pre-heating mode. Keep the paper under when adding food, Be sure not to let the paper contact the heating tube, the temperature of the heating tube is much higher than the heat resisting temperature of the paper.
